===== Inspector =====

qooxdoo inspector is a tool designed to help debugging qooxdoo applications. 

It consists of four separate windows:
1. "console", which is an interactive JavaScript shell.
2. "object finder" which shows a table of all qooxdoo objects.
3. "widget finder" which shows a tree structure of the UI.
4. "property editor" which shows all properties of the currently selected object.


==== How to use it? ====

CTRL + SHIFT + F11 opens all windows
CTRL + SHIFT + F1  opens the console
CTRL + SHIFT + F2  opens the object finder
CTRL + SHIFT + F3  opens the widget finder 
CTRL + SHIFT + F4  opens the property editor
